<td valign="top">
<center>
<p><b>Kings of Israel</b><br />
<i>Main: <a href="/wiki/Kingdom_of_Israel#Royal_Houses_of_Israel" title="Kingdom of Israel" class="mw-redirect">List of the Kings of Israel</a></i><br /></p>
